prodNameC: 卡蒂雅TM SSB(La)抗體檢測試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1.	SSB(La) antigen coated microassay plate: 96 wells, configured in twelve 1x8 strips.
2.	Serum Diluent Type III: Contains buffer, BSA and Tween-20, and proclin (0.1%) as a preservative.
3.	Control: a) High Positive Control: Human serum or defibrinated plasma. Sodium azide (<0.1%) and pen/strep (0.01%) added as preservatives; b) Low Positive Control: Human serum or defibrinated plasma. Sodium azide (<0.1%) and  pen/strep (0.01%) added as preservatives; c) Negative Control: Human serum or defibrinated plasma. Sodium azide (<0.1%) and  pen/strep (0.01%) added to preservatives.
4.	Horseradish-peroxidase (HRP) Conjugate: Goat anti-human IgG, IgA, and IgM containing proclin (0.1%) and gentamicin as preservative. 
5.	Wash Buffer Type II (20x concentrate): Contains TBS, Tween-80 and proclin (0.1%) as a preservative.
6.	Chromogen/Substrate Solution Type I: Tetramethylbenzidine (TMB).
7.	Calibrator: Human serum or defibrinated plasma, sodium azide (<0.1%) and pen/strep (0.01%) added as preservatives.
8.	Stop So
applicantAddr: 新北市板橋區民生路一段三三號六樓之五
efficacy: 以酵素免疫吸著分析法檢測人體血清中SSB(La)抗體。
